videos.description: Darrel Williams catches Danny Etling's pass and then breaks for a big run down the sideline to move LSU into field goal range.
videos.headline: Williams pulls of 63-yard catch and run

videos.description: Derrius Guice breaks off a 59-yard run to move the Tigers down the field then scores a touchdown on the next play giving LSU the lead.
videos.headline: Guice rips off 59-yard run then scores on the next play

videos.description: Danny Etling is sacked by Breeland Speaks for a loss of 10 yards which forces the Tigers to punt.
videos.headline: Ole Miss defense gets drive-ending sack

videos.description: Russell Gage shows off his hops as he jumps over a defender to move the chains for LSU.
videos.headline: Gage hurdles a defender for a 1st down

videos.description: Shea Patterson's deep pass is picked off by Grant Delpit to give the Tigers the ball with 5 minutes left in the first half.
videos.headline: LSU defense stops Ole Miss with interception

videos.description: LSU head coach Ed Orgeron says he likes what he has seen from his running backs but that the team needs more urgency on both sides of the ball.
videos.headline: Orgeron wants team to play with a sense of urgency

videos.description: Ole Miss head coach Matt Luke says that Shea Patterson will play in the second half despite injuring his knee and if he has to come out he's confident in Jordan Ta'amu's play-making ability.
videos.headline: Luke deciding to go with Patterson in 2nd half

videos.description: Derrius Guice finds a hole and runs down the sideline for 48-yards to set up a field goal for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Guice rips off 48-yard run to open the half

videos.description: Danny Etling keeps the ball and runs it into the end zone for a 5-yard touchdown to extend the Tigers lead.
videos.headline: Etling uses legs to score for LSU

videos.description: Jordan Wilkins finds his way through the tackles and runs for 28-yards for a Rebel touchdown cutting the Tigers' lead.
videos.headline: Ole Miss scores on Wilkins TD run

videos.description: Danny Etling pitches it to J. D. Moore who runs up the middle for a touchdown to extend the Tigers lead.
videos.headline: LSU extends lead with catch and run TD

videos.description: Shea Patterson's pass is tipped and then intercepted by John Battle who returns it for 19 yards in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Patterson throws 2nd interception of the night

videos.description: Danny Etling lobs a pass to Foster Moreau who uses his legs to get to the end zone for the 60-yard score.
videos.headline: Etling adds another TD for the Tigers

videos.description: Shea Patterson throws a pass to the sideline and Kevin Toliver II rips it out of the receiver's hands for the third interception for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Toliver pulls off amazing interception

videos.description: LSU RB Derrius Guice discusses his huge performance against Ole Miss as he racked up 276 rushing yards in the win.
videos.headline: Guice owes historic performance to his coaches

videos.description: Derrius Guice rushes for 276 yards and a touchdown to lead LSU past Ole Miss on Saturday.
videos.headline: LSU rolls past Ole Miss
